-- Argentina’s Peso Falls 0.1% in Early Buenos Aires Trading
-- B y   C a m i l a   R u s s o
-- 2011-12-28T13:28:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-28/argentina-s-peso-falls-0-1-in-early-buenos-aires-trading.html
Argentina ’s currency fell after
presidential spokesman Alfredo Scoccimarro said last night
President  Cristina Fernandez de Kirchner  was diagnosed with
thyroid cancer.  The peso weakened 0.1 percent to 4.2990 per dollar at 10:18
a.m. Buenos Aires time.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Camila Russo in Buenos Aires at 
 crusso15@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
